00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:03,080
Englishpod.com

2
00:00:09,920 --> 00:00:14,860
A: Good evening. My name is Fabio, I'll be your waiter for tonight. May I take your order?

3
00:00:14,860 --> 00:00:17,050
B: No, I'm still working on it.

4
00:00:17,050 --> 00:00:20,550
This menu is not even in English. What's good here?

5
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:25,680
A: For you sir, I would recommend spaghetti and meatballs.

6
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:28,040
B: Does it come with coke and fries?

7
00:00:28,840 --> 00:00:34,920
A: It comes with either soup or salad and a complimentary glass of wine, Sir.

8
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,600
B: I'll go with the spaghetti and meatballs, salad and the wine.

9
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:45,240
A: Excellent choice, your order will be ready soon.

10
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:47,200
B: How soon is soon?

11
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:49,040
A: Twenty minutes?

12
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:52,400
B: You know what? I'll just go grab a burger across the street.

